inn2.comm: full ball, BANG! de Villiers hits it into the leg side in the air over midwicket fence.

GONE! another wicket goes, Clarke picks up the wicket, tossed up outside off stump, de Villiers goes for the big shot, mishits it high in the air to wide long on, Hogg moves backwards and takes the catch one handed behind him, wonderful effort to take the catch.
GONE! another wicket goes, short of length, bit more bounce, Hall pulls, gets a top edge, goes high in the air behind the wicket, Gilchrist takes the catch.
